<!-- Templates and Pages -->
<div class="sg-h3 sg-mrg-off--top sg-mrg-half"><a href="templates-pages.html">Templates &amp; Pages</a></div>
<div class="sg-txt">Templates are the master layouts for all the pages in the website, think of them as the scaffolding for the entire website.<br>Pages sit inside templates e.g. "About Us" page.</div>
