<div class="sg-h3 sg-mrg-half">Default Element Styles</div>
<div class="sg-txt sg-mrg-half">All default elements e.g. paragraphs, links, headings, images, etc. are given base styles that define how the element should look in all occurrences on the page. Base styles include setting heading sizes, default link styles, default font styles, etc.</div>
